{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@preconcurrency"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"init"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"unfolding"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"produce"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"attribute","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"attribute","text":"@Sendable"},{"kind":"text","text":" () "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"async"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Element","preciseIdentifier":"s:Scs7Elementxmfp"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"where"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Failure"},{"kind":"text","text":" == any "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Error","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5ErrorP","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Error"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"produce","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A closure that asynchronously produces elements for the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"stream."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this convenience initializer when you have an asynchronous function"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that can produce elements for the stream, and don’t want to invoke"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a continuation manually. This initializer “unfolds” your closure into"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a full-blown asynchronous stream. The created stream handles adherence to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AsyncSequence"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol automatically. To terminate the stream with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"an error, throw the error from your closure."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following example shows an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AsyncThrowingStream"},{"type":"text","text":" created with this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"initializer that produces random numbers on a one-second interval. If the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"random number is divisible by 5 with no remainder, the stream throws a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MyRandomNumberError"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["let stream = AsyncThrowingStream<Int, Error> {","    await Task.sleep(1 * 1_000_000_000)","    let random = Int.random(in: 1...10)","    if random % 5 == 0 {","        throw MyRandomNumberError()","    }","    return random","}","","// Call point:","do {","    for try await random in stream {","        print(random)","    }","} catch {","    print(error)","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["/documentation/swift/asyncthrowingstream/init(unfolding:)"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift","doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncThrowingStream"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Constructs an asynchronous throwing stream from a given element-producing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"closure.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Initializer","title":"init(unfolding:)","externalID":"s:Scs9unfoldingScsyxs5Error_pGxSgyYaKc_tcsAB_pRs_rlufc","symbolKind":"init","fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"unfolding","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@Sendable","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" () ","kind":"text"},{"text":"async","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Element","preciseIdentifier":"s:Scs7Elementxmfp","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"modules":[{"relatedModules":[],"name":"Swift"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncThrowingStream/init(unfolding:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncThrowingStream":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"AsyncThrowingStream"}],"url":"/documentation/swift/asyncthrowingstream","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An asynchronous sequence generated from an error-throwing closure that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calls a continuation to produce new elements."}],"identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncThrowingStream","type":"topic","title":"AsyncThrowingStream","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"AsyncThrowingStream"}]},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Error":{"fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Error","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type representing an error value that can be thrown."}],"url":"/documentation/swift/error","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Error","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Error","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Error"},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncThrowingStream/init(unfolding:)":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncThrowingStream/init(unfolding:)","type":"topic","title":"init(unfolding:)","kind":"symbol","url":"/documentation/swift/asyncthrowingstream/init(unfolding:)","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"unfolding"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"attribute","text":"@Sendable"},{"kind":"text","text":" () "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"async"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Scs7Elementxmfp","text":"Element"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Constructs an asynchronous throwing stream from a given element-producing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"closure."}]},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift":{"identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift","type":"topic","url":"/documentation/swift","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Build apps using a powerful open language.","type":"text"}],"title":"Swift"}}}